# Our Services

# 1. General Physician Consultation
Includes:
- Diagnosis of common illnesses
- Fever, cold, and infection treatment
- Blood pressure and diabetes monitoring
- Lifestyle guidance

Why Choose Us:
We take time to understand your symptoms and provide clear treatment guidance without rushing.


# 2. Preventive Health Check-ups
Includes:
- Basic and advanced health packages
- Blood tests
- Diabetes screening
- Heart health screening

Why Choose Us:
Early detection helps prevent serious health problems. Our same-day reports ensure quick action.


# 3. In-House Laboratory Services
Includes:
- Blood tests
- Urine tests
- Thyroid tests
- Lipid profile
- Complete blood count (CBC)

Why Choose Us:
Get consultation and lab testing in one place without unnecessary delays.


# 4. Senior Citizen Care
Includes:
- Chronic disease monitoring
- Medication review
- Regular health tracking
- Lifestyle and diet advice

Why Choose Us:
We provide extra care and comfort for elderly patients.


# 5. Family and Child Care
Includes:
- Routine health check-ups
- Growth monitoring
- Minor illness treatment
- Vaccination guidance

Why Choose Us:
Parents trust us because we explain everything clearly and treat children gently.


